<DocLayout title="CLI Commands" description="Complete reference for all Erold CLI commands.">
  <h1>CLI Commands Reference</h1>

  <p>
    Complete list of all available CLI commands.
  </p>

  <h2>Task Commands</h2>

  <h3>erold task list</h3>
  <p>List tasks in a project.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold task list [--project PROJECT] [--status STATUS] [--assignee USER]

# Examples
erold task list
erold task list --status todo
erold task list --project MYAPP --status in_progress`}</code></pre>

  <h3>erold task create</h3>
  <p>Create a new task.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold task create TITLE [--project PROJECT] [--priority PRIORITY] [--label LABEL]

# Examples
erold task create "Implement auth"
erold task create "Fix bug" --priority high --label bug
erold task create "Add tests" --project MYAPP --assignee @me`}</code></pre>

  <h3>erold task show</h3>
  <p>Show task details.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold task show TASK_ID

# Example
erold task show MYAPP-123`}</code></pre>

  <h3>erold task update</h3>
  <p>Update a task.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold task update TASK_ID [--status STATUS] [--priority PRIORITY] [--assignee USER]

# Examples
erold task update MYAPP-123 --status done
erold task update MYAPP-123 --priority urgent --assignee john@example.com`}</code></pre>

  <h3>erold task delete</h3>
  <p>Delete a task.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold task delete TASK_ID [--force]

# Example
erold task delete MYAPP-123`}</code></pre>

  <h2>Project Commands</h2>

  <h3>erold project list</h3>
  <p>List all projects.</p>
  <pre><code>erold project list</code></pre>

  <h3>erold project create</h3>
  <p>Create a new project.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold project create NAME --key KEY [--description DESC]

# Example
erold project create "My App" --key MYAPP --description "Main product"`}</code></pre>

  <h3>erold project show</h3>
  <p>Show project details and statistics.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold project show PROJECT_KEY

# Example
erold project show MYAPP`}</code></pre>

  <h2>Knowledge Base Commands</h2>

  <h3>yet kb list</h3>
  <p>List knowledge items.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold kb list [--prefix PREFIX]

# Examples
yet kb list
yet kb list --prefix api/`}</code></pre>

  <h3>yet kb get</h3>
  <p>Get a knowledge item.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold kb get KEY

# Example
yet kb get architecture`}</code></pre>

  <h3>yet kb set</h3>
  <p>Create or update a knowledge item.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold kb set KEY CONTENT

# Examples
yet kb set architecture "Microservices with Node.js..."
yet kb set api/auth "JWT tokens with 24h expiry..."

# From file
yet kb set architecture --file ./docs/architecture.md`}</code></pre>

  <h3>yet kb delete</h3>
  <p>Delete a knowledge item.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold kb delete KEY

# Example
yet kb delete old-docs`}</code></pre>

  <h3>yet kb search</h3>
  <p>Search the knowledge base.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold kb search QUERY

# Example
yet kb search "authentication"`}</code></pre>

  <h2>Configuration Commands</h2>

  <h3>erold config set</h3>
  <p>Set a configuration value.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold config set KEY VALUE

# Examples
erold config set defaultProject MYAPP
erold config set format json`}</code></pre>

  <h3>erold config get</h3>
  <p>Get a configuration value.</p>
  <pre><code>erold config get defaultProject</code></pre>

  <h3>erold config list</h3>
  <p>List all configuration.</p>
  <pre><code>erold config list</code></pre>

  <h2>Other Commands</h2>

  <h3>erold login</h3>
  <p>Authenticate with your API key.</p>
  <pre><code>{`erold login [--key KEY]

# Interactive
erold login

# With key
erold login --key yet_xxx`}</code></pre>

  <h3>yet logout</h3>
  <p>Remove stored credentials.</p>
  <pre><code>yet logout</code></pre>

  <h3>erold whoami</h3>
  <p>Show current user and tenant.</p>
  <pre><code>erold whoami</code></pre>

